snippet.title: Georgia Confronts Amber... | Love Island 2017
snippet.description:
After an explosive recoupling it's time for Georgia to face Amber (we don't envy her). But boy does this girl have balls as she confronts the new enemy... It's fair to say Amber is more than a little bit annoyed that the new girl chose to pair up with her Kem. No one comes between Kember you know... Oops, we must've forgotten to give Georgia that memo.
